high_descs: Go to the left to the table with a loaf of bread on it.
Pick up the spoon near the bread on the table.
Turn around and turn left to go to the sink.
Open the cabinet under the sink and put the spoon on the plate.
Pick up the plate with a spoon in it.
Turn around and turn right to go back to the table again.
Put the plate and the spoon next to the bread on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate that has a spoon in it ,next to to bread on the table.

high_descs: Turn left and face the table on your left
Pick up the spoon on the table edge
Turn right and head to the sink cabinet on your right
Open the sink cabinet then put the spoon in the bowl
Pick up the bowl with spoon then close the cabinet
Turn left then head to the table
Put the bowl with spoon on the table
anns.task_desc: Put the bowl with spoon on the table

high_descs: Turn and go to the table.
Pick up a spoon on the table.
Turn and go to the sink.
Put the spoon on the plate in the sink.
Pick up the plate in the sink.
Go to the table.
Put the plate on the table.
anns.task_desc: Move a plate from the sink to the table.
